»CL9:Where and when?
»CL8:---------------

»CL0:The party will be held in a big hall called Amperhalle, in Emmering near
Fürstenfeldbruck (munich/germany)
This conference is a 100% LEGAL party. That means that copying or using
cracked software is under NO circumstances tolerable.

Starting on »CL8:Friday the 27th of October (15:30 noon)» and ending on »CL8:Sunday 
the 29th of October (12:00)».

Since the Comparade is an Amiga and C64 party, only Amiga and C64 are allowed
(Atari and Archimedes allowed though)



























